.TH PIXIE 1 "April 2026" "pixie 1.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
pixie \- minimal static HTTP server
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B pixie
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBpixie\fR starts a static HTTP server using runtime configuration from:
.IP \(bu 2
\fBPIXIE_CONFIG\fR (if set)
.IP \(bu 2
\fB./config-pixie.yml\fR
.IP \(bu 2
\fB/etc/pixie/config-pixie.yml\fR
.PP
Web content root is resolved from:
.IP \(bu 2
\fBPIXIE_WEB_ROOT\fR (if set and valid)
.IP \(bu 2
development \fB../web\fR
.IP \(bu 2
\fB/usr/share/pixie/web\fR
.SH FILES
.TP
.B /etc/pixie/config-pixie.yml
System-wide runtime configuration file.
.TP
.B /usr/share/pixie/web
Default static web root.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Normal exit.
.TP
.B 2
Configuration initialization error.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR systemd (1)
